data.text:
Two Of A Kind

Frankie and Mike are caught in the middle of a long standing family feud. Meanwhile, a fearful Sue receives her first detention ever for being caught going off campus for lunch.

My Brother, My Keeper

Waiting on an answer from Carla, Turk spends time with his brother, who confesses he's getting a divorce. JD works with an old colleague of Dr Kelso, while Jordan and Dr Cox have a disagreement over finding out their baby's sex.

Welcome Back Duke

A former con man's rusty magic leads to disaster. Meanwhile, Sabrina auditions for the school musical.

Negative Reaction

Photographer Paul Galesko plans to murder his domineering wife Frances, and pin the crime on an ex-convict named Alvin Deschler. Galesko's plan is to make it look as though Alvin kidnapped his wife and killed her.
